{
  "texts": [
    "This enables the model to analyze and comprehend the spatial relationships between different image regions.",
    "Itis an effective architecture for image classification and computer vision tasks.",
    "Images are processed through the Transformer model, consisting of spatial attention and a feed-forward neural network.",
    "The spatial attention mechanism applies the attention to the image pixels, followed by the feed-forward neural network to the output of the attention mechanism.",
    "In addition, this modeluses a patch-based strategy where an image is divided into smaller segments and learns to focus separately on each patch."
  ]
}